author: National Economic and Development Authority - Systems Data and Analysis Division
name: cost-overruns-of-active-oda-loan-assisted-project
notes: Provides quarterly information on the amount of cost increases or overruns incurred by active ODA Loan-assisted projects. In addition to the amount and percentage of cost increase or overrun, the dataset contains other project information such as the development partner, implementing agency, previous ICC-approved cost, revised cost, reason(s) for the cost increase or overrun, status, and ICC or NEDA Board action.

resources.name: Cost-overruns of Active ODA Loan-assisted Projects  as of Sep 30 2014 (Dataset).csv

title: Cost-overruns of Active ODA Loan-assisted Projects
